    "JHEP03(2024)049 JHEP03(2024)049The most crucial point to emphasize from this analysis is that the upper bounds in eq.",
    "(4.2) are not particularly stringent: they are all well above the size one would expect if the corresponding effective operators were generated beyond the tree level.",
